com.travelbank.knit.schedulers

Class IOScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.travelbank.knit.schedulers.IOScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SchedulerInterface

    public class IOScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
implements SchedulerInterface
    This scheduler is meant to handle all simple IO operations such as Rest calls and Database look ups. It uses a ThreadPoolExecutor provided by KnitIOThreadPool to distribute tasks to other threads.
